te Facts]\u2014[[United States Department of Agriculture|USDA]]\n* {{curlie|Regional/North_America/United_States/North_Dakota}}\n* {{osmrelation-inline|161653}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Colorado]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of U.S. states by date of admission to the Union]]|years=Admitted on November 2, 1889 (39th)}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[South Dakota]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = <span style=\"font-size:11pt;\">Topics related to North Dakota</span><br />''The Peace Garden State''\n|list =\n{{North Dakota|expanded}}\n{{Protected areas of North Dakota}}\n{{Midwestern United States}}\n{{New France}}\n{{New Spain}}\n{{United States political divisions}}\n|state=expanded}}\n\n{{Coord|display=title|47|N|100|W|region:US-ND_type:adm1st_scale:3000000}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:North Dakota| ]]\n[[Category:Midwestern United States]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1889]]\n[[Category:States of the United States]]\n[[Category:U.S. states with multiple time zones]]\n[[Category:1889 establishments in the United States]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|the U.S. state of North Dakota}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=August 2017}}\n{{Infobox U.S. state\n|name                    = North Dakota\n|official_name           = State of North Dakota\n|image_flag              = Flag of North Dakota.svg\n|flag_link               = Flag of North Dakota\n|image_seal              = NorthDakota-StateSeal.svg\n|seal_link               = Great Seal of North Dakota\n|image_map               = North Dakota in United States.svg\n|nickname                = Peace Garden State,<br />Roughrider State, Flickertail State\n|motto                   = Liberty and Union, Now and Forever, One and Inseparable\t\n|anthem                  = [[North Dakota Hymn]]\n|Former                  = Dakota Territory\n|population_demonym      = North Dakotan\n|seat                    = [[Bismarck, North Dakota|Bismarck]]\n|LargestCity             = [[Fargo, North Dakota|Fargo]]\n|Lar